Package: trenchchat
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libxcb-cursor0, libxcb1, libx11-6, libgl1
Replaces: trenchchat
Conflicts: trenchchat
Maintainer: TrenchChat <https://github.com/HunterL31/TrenchChat>
Homepage: https://github.com/HunterL31/TrenchChat
Description: Decentralised encrypted mesh chat over Reticulum
 TrenchChat is a peer-to-peer encrypted chat application built on the
 Reticulum network stack and LXMF messaging protocol. It supports
 channel-based group messaging, offline message sync, and invite-only
 channels with role-based permissions.
 .
 User data (identity keys, channels, message history) is stored in
 ~/.trenchchat/ and is preserved across upgrades.
